data.name: EntryPointDBox.ToolTip
data.value: Select the entry point file you want your bot to use NTBot - standard or solo botting experience NTLeader - for running games and have leechers or followers NTLeecher - this will aid in joining yours or other peoples games NTRusher - Rush other characters through a difficulty NTManual - Manual playing with extras AMSLeader - Automuling items and supports leechers AMSLeecher -Automuling while leeching games
